WEBVTT

1
00:36:25.710 --> 00:36:27.830 
- 你不记得我了?  - 嗯?
- Don't you remember me?  - Huh?

2
00:36:27.920 --> 00:36:29.830 
战争中 你救了我的命啊
The war. You saved my life.

3
00:36:29.920 --> 00:36:32.210 
- 我?  - 奇怪了
- Me?  - Strange.

4
00:36:32.300 --> 00:36:34.840 
我一直认为你是雅利安人呢
And I always thought of you as an Aryan.

5
00:36:34.920 --> 00:36:36.880 
- 我是个吃素的人  - 唉 你真想不起来了?
- I'm a vegetarian.  - Well, don't you remember?

6
00:36:36.970 --> 00:36:39.930 
敌人要抓住我们 但是我们用飞机逃脱了
The enemy tried to capture us, but we got away in my plane.

7
00:36:40.010 --> 00:36:41.430 
飞机?
Plane?

8
00:36:41.510 --> 00:36:44.100 
然后飞机坠毁了
And then we crashed.

9
00:36:44.180 --> 00:36:45.850 
坠...
Cra...

10
00:36:48.440 --> 00:36:50.440 
噢...!对啊
Oh, yes.

11
00:36:50.520 --> 00:36:52.190 
我想起来了
Now I remember.

12
00:36:53.780 --> 00:36:56.320 
- 噢 你还好吗?  - 我这位朋友做了什么?
- Well, how are you?  - What has my friend done?

